722406f-a.title: Manhattan: Park Avenue - 130th Street (East)
722406f-a.text:
Park Ave., west side, north from, and including East 130th Street.
The 6-story building, in the foreground, is at the N.W. corner of East 130th
Street, and is occupied by small manufacturing establishments.
December 16, 1936.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REP ODUCTIONS.
